{"tid":1392333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呼籲香港空運業同行8月5日一齊罷工！","createTime":"2019-07-31T16:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T11:47:47.000Z","uid":61106,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4739c59575450c42784c67d7ff2b7588fda6b334","tid":1392333,"uid":61106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:59:44.000Z","msg":"致香港空運業同行：<br />\n<br />\n我係一位香港空運貨站有限公司嘅員工。相信大家呢兩個月從不同媒體都睇到好多觸目驚心，令人髮指嘅畫面。由「反送中大遊行」、「元朗西鐵站暴力事件」、「警黑合作」至「義士被捕」，種種事件都表示今時今日嘅香港已經唔係香港人熟悉嘅香港。<br />\n<br />\n在「元朗西鐵暴力事件」中，警察在從得悉有白衣人聚集並手持武器後，仍然無動於衷，任由白衣暴徒無差別暴打香港市民。相反對於手無寸鐵嘅示威人士則以防暴警察以不合理武力暴打，並以暴力罪控告示威人士。警察到底係黑社會？還是為市民服務？<br />\n<br />\n在國際上已經有大量證據顯示「警黑合作」。香港人嘅人權、言論自由、集會自由，甚至人生安全已經受到嚴重損害。在這個大事大非嘅前提下，香港人不應該再沉默，應該以行動去守護屬於香港人嘅自由。我地同白衣暴徒和黑警並不一樣，至少我地仲有良知。<br />\n<br />\n在這個一啲底線都無嘅政權底下，竟然「警黑合作」，損害香港自由和法治，香港人並唔需要為自己定下底線。<br />\n<br />\n我在此呼籲香港空運業同行8月5日一齊罷工，迫使香港政府回應香港人五大訴求！<br />\n<br />\nFreedom is not free!<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n一位仲有良知嘅普通香港人上<br />\n2019年8月1日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y1QbVVP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY1QbVVP.png&h=3493b81e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb20cb4d1b3385b4fc4abea7b82659193f82b224","tid":1392333,"uid":64193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee70caea6dc36ee58bec7082737a2acb7ef34605","tid":1392333,"uid":61106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb20cb4d1b3385b4fc4abea7b82659193f82b224","tid":1392333,"uid":64193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:10:12.000Z","msg":"機場絕對係好地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f66101ec318de5b183e4c089e43a41d739f6bbe","tid":1392333,"uid":1612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:12:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UfXqfrD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUfXqfrD.png&h=8f3dee07&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vZtQrBo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvZtQrBo.png&h=9c34613e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lr1iAst.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLr1iAst.png&h=ad9ecde7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UK1eTd8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUK1eTd8.png&h=9898c97d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02a1d8eb320f77ce65f701759204344fa58d5263","tid":1392333,"uid":61106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:06:31.000Z","msg":"推到空運行業大罷工"},{"pid":"5d9aadab659bd2da75e94d38719cf5c6b631d2b6","tid":1392333,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb20cb4d1b3385b4fc4abea7b82659193f82b224","tid":1392333,"uid":64193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdea092bfbbe402e85c217f12e0009321a4af519","tid":1392333,"uid":8486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:09:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"301fc8610947a26e9c6b161c517fa76018fff886","tid":1392333,"uid":65289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af8247e2f3b3e02e3c5f1f3cf166685e7e97553","tid":1392333,"uid":61106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:45:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"p